OL,3,CStarmer faces backbench anger after
OL,4,C'day one' workers' right U-turn
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer is facing backbench
OL,7,Fanger after ministers abandoned plans
OL,8,Fto give workers day-one protection
OL,9,Fagainst unfair dismissal in a U-turn
OL,10,Fthat breaches the Labour manifesto.
OL,12,FMPs including a former minister who
OL,13,Fspearheaded the Employment Rights Bill
OL,14,Fwith ex-deputy leader Angela Rayner
OL,15,Fvoiced concerns over the climbdown
OL,16,Fannounced by the Government on
OL,17,FThursday night.
