OL,6,FThe Government now intends to
OL,7,Fintroduce the right after six months
OL,8,Fof service instead, while other day-
OL,9,Fone rights to paternity leave and sick
OL,10,Fpay are still set to go ahead, coming
OL,11,Finto effect in April 2026.
OL,13,FLabour's manifesto explicitly promised
OL,14,Fto "consult fully with businesses,
OL,15,Fworkers, and civil society on how to
OL,16,Fput our plans into practice before
OL,17,Flegislation is passed".
