OL,6,F"This will include banning
OL,7,Fexploitative zero-hours contracts;
OL,8,Fending fire and rehire; and
OL,9,Fintroducing basic rights from day one
OL,10,Fto parental leave, sick pay, and
OL,11,Fprotection from unfair dismissal," it
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FThe concession, which comes after some
OL,15,Fbusinesses voiced concerns about
OL,16,Fpotential costs and recruitment
OL,17,Fchallenges, sparked an immediate
OL,18,Fbacklash among some backbenchers and
OL,19,Fthe Unite union.
