OL,7,FThornaby East, Andy McDonald, branded
OL,8,Fthe move a "complete betrayal" and
OL,9,Fvowed to push for its reversal.
OL,11,FHe said: "we cannot support that
OL,12,Fhalfway measure", adding: "This is a
OL,13,Fwrong-headed move and I will campaign
OL,14,Fto have this concession reversed."
OL,16,FLabour MP for Poole, Neil Duncan-
OL,17,FJordan, told the Press Association:
OL,18,F"There has been no discussion with the
OL,19,FPLP about this.
